title: JBT Corporation Announces Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call Schedule
text:
JBT Corporation
CHICAGO , Oct. 8, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- JBT Corporation (NYSE: JBT) will report third quarter 2015 financial results after the market closes on Tuesday, October 27, 2015 . A conference call is scheduled for 10:00 a.m. EDT on Wednesday, October 28, 2015 .
Participants may access the conference call using the following numbers:
U.S. and Canada:
(877) 235-3250
International:
+1 (706) 643-5005
Conference ID #:
56776962
The call will be simultaneously webcast on JBT Corporation's Investor Relations website, which can be accessed at http://ir.jbtcorporation.com . To participate on the webcast, please log on to the website at least ten minutes before the call to register.
An online audio replay of the conference call will be available on JBT Corporation's Investor Relations website at approximately 1:30 p.m. EDT on October 28 , 2015.
JBT Corporation (NYSE: JBT) is a leading global technology solutions provider to the food processing and air transportation industries. JBT Corporation designs, manufactures, tests, and services technologically sophisticated systems and products for regional and multi-national industrial food processing customers through its JBT FoodTech segment and for domestic and international air transportation customers through its JBT AeroTech segment. JBT Corporation employs approximately 4,200 people worldwide and operates sales, service, manufacturing and sourcing operations located in over 25 countries. For more information, please visit http://www.jbtcorporation.com .
